118 /** helper function that sets up everything for the test in #testFTSK_CreateTasks() */
119 void helperCreateStatic(const char *pTaskName, OS_TASK_HANDLE handleToBeReturned) {
120  MPU_xTaskCreateStatic_ExpectAndReturn(NULL_PTR, pTaskName, 0u, 0u, 0u, NULL_PTR, NULL_PTR, handleToBeReturned);
121  MPU_xTaskCreateStatic_IgnoreArg_pxTaskCode();
122  MPU_xTaskCreateStatic_IgnoreArg_ulStackDepth();
123  MPU_xTaskCreateStatic_IgnoreArg_pvParameters();
124  MPU_xTaskCreateStatic_IgnoreArg_uxPriority();
125  MPU_xTaskCreateStatic_IgnoreArg_puxStackBuffer();
126  MPU_xTaskCreateStatic_IgnoreArg_pxTaskBuffer();
127 }
